{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2014-01-03---angularjs-scroll-to-element-using-directives/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Nadeem Khedr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6c4ed132-a635-57ed-bec8-b21d5d38f876","excerpt":"I want to implement a simple concept using angular, scrolling to a specific area of the page using a directive, I found myself needing this in a pagination…","html":"<p>I want to implement a simple concept using angular, scrolling to a specific area of the page using a directive, I found myself needing this in a pagination example, I want to scroll to the top of the list when the user clicks on next page</p>\n<p>Whenever I am trying to implement a directive like that I always try to first write how I would want to represent it in the html.</p>\n<p><strong>To checkout a demo go <a href=\"http://plnkr.co/edit/WmxLJy2VWWJ69WMAz8am\">here</a></strong></p>\n<p>I want my html in the end to be something like this</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>def<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scroll-bookmark</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Default<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bm1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scroll-bookmark</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bookmark1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Bookmark 1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bm2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scroll-bookmark</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bookmark2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Bookmark 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>btns<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scroll-to-bookmark</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Default bookmark<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scroll-to-bookmark</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bookmark1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Bookmark 1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scroll-to-bookmark</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bookmark2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Bookmark 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>So there is two parts that makes this example</p>\n<p><strong><code class=\"language-text\">scroll-bookmark</code></strong>\nIs Where I want to scroll to <em>(I want to register how I would get there)</em></p>\n<p><strong><code class=\"language-text\">scroll-to-bookmark</code></strong>\nThis is the actual directive, I want when I click here to scroll to the corespondent <code class=\"language-text\">scroll-bookmark</code> with the same value <em>(default one if there is no value)</em></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">angular<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">module</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'MyApp'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">directive</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'scrollToBookmark'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function-variable function\">link</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">scope<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> element<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> attrs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> attrs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>scrollToBookmark<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">click</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        scope<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">$apply</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> selector <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[scroll-bookmark='\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span> value <span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token string\">\"']\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n          <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>selector<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n          <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scrollTo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> element<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>offsetTop – <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">// Don’t want the top to be the exact element, -100 will go to the top for a little bit more</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"AngularJs Scroll to element using directives","date":"January 03, 2014","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2013-11-25---how-to-do-authorization-and-role-based-permissions-in-angularjs/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"How to do Authorization and Role  based permissions in AngularJs"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2014-02-22---why-sass-is-awesome-make-an-elegant-button-with-only-one-color-to-generate/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Why SASS is awesome, make an elegant button with only one color to generate"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"6c4ed132-a635-57ed-bec8-b21d5d38f876","previousPostId":"f1e7081e-2381-5697-938f-fb2d4580d1b0","nextPostId":"36e15772-4565-5ef7-b64b-971ba9923684"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}